        "action": "Require and fund CCTV to be installed at all children's play areas",
        "additional_details": "I believe this will help protect our children from harm and give them a safe place to play, prevent crime and anti-social behaviour.\r\n \r\nI feel having CCTV on all parks and play areas would help discourage anyone approaching children at parks and also help the police in identifying any suspects of crime.",
        "background": "The Government should fund and require local authorities to install CCTV on all children\u2019s play areas, including playgrounds, to help protect children.",
